                          <p style="height:30px;color:white;background-color:#0066CC;border:1px;">This page has been archived and commenting is disabled.</p>                        <h1 class="title">Gold At $1600, Recoupling With Stocks Post QE2</h1>
            <div class="tabs"></div>
            <div class="node">
  <div class="picture">
  <a href="/users/tyler-durden" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-5.jpg" alt="Tyler Durden&#039;s picture" title="Tyler Durden&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>

  
  <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/users/tyler-durden">Tyler Durden</a> on  02/15/2013 12:00 -0400</span><br /><br /><span class="taxonomy"></span><br /><br />

      <div class="clear-block clear"></div>
    <div class="js-links">
