<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3247589">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Fri, 02/15/2013 - 16:26 | <a href="/news/2013-02-15/gold-1600-recoupling-stocks-post-qe2#comment-3247589" class="active">3247589</a></span>
