<p><strong>QED If you think a pound is money then you are a Slave.</strong></p>
<p><strong>QED If you think a gold coin is money then I would say that I agree with your IDEA of money.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Fiat currency is useful for exchange and a unit of account. However, in the long run, it is worthless.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Gold is useful as a store of value. It likes to sit still. </strong><strong>However, in the long run, it is immortal. I can only hope mankind is immortal too.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Money is an idea we may out grow.<br /></strong></p>
